cu.explanation_en: Setting local_s_portc to 99999 exceeds the maximum allowed port number, causing F1 interface setup failure and preventing proper CU-DU communication.

du.explanation_en: Setting preambleReceivedTargetPower to 100 exceeds the maximum allowed power level, causing configuration validation failure and preventing proper RACH setup.
du.explanation_zh: 將 preambleReceivedTargetPower 設定為 100 超過最大允許功率水平，會導致配置驗證失敗，並阻止正確的 RACH 設置。
